4. Expressly Permitted Paid Services and Customer Work
------------------------------------------------------
Subject to the rest of this License, You may charge fees for Professional Services involving the
Software or a Derivative Work, including fees for installation, configuration, customization,
integration, development, migration, training, support, maintenance, and customer-specific
delivery or operation.

You may also Distribute or operate unmodified or modified copies of the Software for a specific
customer, including through a Dedicated Customer Deployment, if all of the following are true:

(a) the recipient receives the Software or Derivative Work under this License;

(b) You comply with Section 3;

(c) the commercial value of Your offer arises primarily from Professional Services,
customer-specific customization, integration, deployment, support, or other customer-specific
work, and not from access to a generally available product or service that would otherwise be a
Competitive Offering; and

(d) if You operate the Software or a Derivative Work for the customer, that deployment is a
Dedicated Customer Deployment.

For clarity, merely labeling something as "services", "support", "implementation", or
"managed deployment" does not make it permitted if, in substance, You are commercializing a
Competitive Offering.

