5.2 Offer a Competing Hosted or Managed Service.
Offer or provide the Software or a Derivative Work as a hosted, managed, SaaS, API, platform,
or similar service to third parties, except as expressly permitted by Section 4.

5.3 Sell or White-Label a Competing Product.
Sell, license, sublicense, rent, lease, distribute, white-label, OEM, or otherwise commercialize
the Software or a Derivative Work as a standalone, general-purpose, or generally available
